snippet: The U.S. Senate passed legislation on Monday seeking to bar Iran's proposed U.N. ambassador, Hamid Abutalebi, from entering the United States....

headline.print_headline: Senate Votes to Bar Proposed Iran U.N. Ambassador From Country
headline.main: Senate Votes to Bar Proposed Iran U.N. Ambassador From Country

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Senate passed legislation on Monday seeking to bar Iran's proposed U.N. ambassador, Hamid Abutalebi, from entering the United States.
